iwan-based%20chipmaking%20giant.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ec73837-0d25-40f4-862a-575baa6227ed%5C%22%3ETrump%20has%20strong%20views%20on%20Taiwan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20potential%20threat%20hanging%20over%20Taiwan%20from%20China%20adds%20to%20the%20precarious%20state%20of%20the%20chip%20industry.%20That's%20because%20most%20big%20tech%20companies%2C%20including%20Apple%2C%20rely%20on%20TSMC%20to%20make%20the%20chips%20they%20design.%20Trump%20sees%20this%20dynamic%20as%20problematic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaiwan%2C%20they%20stole%20our%20chip%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Rogan%20in%20the%20same%20podcast%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETSMC%20is%20the%20only%20company%20that%20can%20reliably%20make%20the%20most%20cutting-edge%20chips%20at%20scale.%20Intel%20has%20struggled%20to%20successfully%20manufacture%20these%20advanced%20chips%20or%20even%20the%20smaller%20components%20they%20require.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-second-trump-term-means-for-intel-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730934162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672bc3815ec9bfa3d63c2c8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-second-trump-term-means-for-intel-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump's%20love%20of%20tariffs%20and%20his%20tough%20comments%20on%20Taiwan%20have%20big%20implications%20for%20Intel%20and%20the%20entire%20semiconductor%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%20(Emma%20Cosgrove)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-second-trump-term-means-for-intel-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20Night%202024%20Coverage%20Draws%2042.3%20Million%20Viewers%2C%20Down%20Over%2025%25%20From%202020%22%2C