20fuelled%20this%20campaign.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20concede%20the%20election%2C%20I%20do%20not%20concede%20the%20fight%20that%20fuelled%20this%20campaign.%20Fight%20for%20freedom%2C%20opportunity%2C%20dignity%20for%20all%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Harris%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20that%20lasted%20less%20than%2015%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20supporters%20cheered%2C%20even%20though%20she%20admitted%20it%20was%20painful%20to%20lose.%20She%20told%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bkeep%20fighting%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20will%20close%20with%20this.%20Only%20when%20it%20is%20dark%20enough%2C%20can%20you%20see%20the%20stars.%20I%20know%20many%20people%20feel%20we%20are%20entering%20a%20dark%20time...%20Let%20us%20fill%20the%20sky%20with%20the%20light%20of%20billions%20and%20billions%20of%20stars%2C%20the%20light%20of%20truth%2C%20optimism%20and%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20outcome%20of%20this%20election%20is%20not%20what%20we%20wanted%2C%20not%20what%20we%20fought%20for%2C%20not%20what%20we%20voted%20for%2C%20but%20hear%20me%20when%20I%20say%20that%20the%20light%20of%20America's%20promise%20will%20always%20burn%20bright%20as%20long%20as%20we%20never%20give%20up%20and%20as%20long%20as%20we%20keep%20fighting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20accept%20the%20results%20of%20this%20election.%20Earlier%20today%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20President-elect%20Trump%20and%20congratulated%20him%20on%20his%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Harris%20told%20supporters%20in%20the%20concession%20speech%20at%20her%20alma%20mater%20Howard%20University%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20told%20him%20that%20we%20will%20help%20him%20and%20his%20team%20with%20their%20transition%2C%20and%20that%20we%20will%20engage%20in%20a%20peaceful%20transfer%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump's%20victory%2C%20fol