2C%20space%20and%20several%20other%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20and%20Vice%20President-elect%20JD%20Vance%20have%20scoffed%20at%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20US%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%20under%20outgoing%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20with%20their%20aides%20musing%20about%20forcing%20Ukraine%20to%20make%20concessions%20to%20end%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20congratulated%20Trump%20and%20said%20he%20hoped%20the%20new%20US%20leader%20would%20help%20Ukraine%20find%20a%20%26quot%3Bjust%20peace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Harris%20entered%20the%20race%20in%20July%20after%20the%20visibly%20ageing%20Biden%20dropped%20out.%20She%20ran%20a%20centrist%20campaign%20that%20highlighted%20Mr%20Trump's%20inflammatory%20messaging%20and%20use%20of%20racist%20and%20sexist%20tropes.%20But%20his%20apocalyptic%20warnings%20about%20immigration%20found%20their%20mark%20with%20voters%20battered%20by%20the%20post-Covid%20economy%20and%20eager%20for%20change%20after%20the%20Biden%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730930520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fkm2lfqfg_kamala-harris_625x300_07_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fharris-concedes-election-to-trump-outcome-not-what-we-wanted-but-light-of-americas-promise-will-always-burn-bright-6960835%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20conceded%20the%20presidential%20election%20to%20Donald%20Trump%20after%20an%20acrimonious%2C%20turbulent%20and%20polarising%20campaign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fharris-concedes-election-to-trump-outcome-not-what-we-wanted-but-light-of-americas-promise-will-always-burn-bright-6960835%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20t