20penne%20recipe.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20whip%20up%20her%20five-cheese%20penne%2C%20you'll%20need%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E1%2F2%20cup%20freshly%20grated%20pecorino%20Romano%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%2F2%20cup%20shredded%20Italian%20fontina%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%2F4%20cup%20crumbled%20Italian%20Gorgonzola%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%2F4%20pound%20fresh%20mozzarella%2C%20sliced%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20tablespoons%20ricotta%20cheese%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20should%20admit%20that%20I%20got%20Romano%20cheese%20instead%20of%20pecorino%20Romano%2C%20which%20I%20couldn't%20find%20in%20my%20local%20supermarket's%20little%20fromagerie%20no%20matter%20how%20hard%20I%20tried.%20I%20did%20a%20quick%20Google%20search%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BIs%20pecorino%20the%20same%20as%20Romano%3F%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20was%20convinced%20that%20they%20were%20basically%20identical.%20I%20later%20learned%20that%20the%20Romano%20I%20had%20purchased%20was%20actually%20made%20with%20cow's%20milk%2C%20while%20pecorino%20Romano%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cheese.com%2Fromano%2F%5C%22%3Eis%20always%20made%20with%20sheep's%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20alas%2C%20they're%20both%20still%20in%20the%20same%20family%20and%20known%20for%20their%20sharp%20flavors%2C%20so%20I%20think%20the%20cheese%20gods%20will%20forgive%20me%20on%20this%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGarten's%20five-cheese%20penne%20also%20requires%20four%20additional%20ingredients.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten's%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f63a31c57b7da001ee124a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou'll%20also%20need%20heavy%20cream%2C%20crushed%20tomatoes%2C%20basil%2C%20and%20penne.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20all%20that%20cheese%2C%20you'll%20need%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E1%20pound%20penne%20rigate%20pasta%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20cups%20heavy%20cream%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20cup%20crushed%20tomatoes%20in%20thick%20tomato%20puree%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E6%20fresh%20basil%20leaves%2C%20chopped%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETo%20prep%2C%20I%20preheated%20my%20oven%20to%20500%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20and%20started%20grating%20and%20measuring%20my%20cheeses.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten's%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f63a30557b7da001ee1249b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20grated%20my%20cheeses%20and%20used%20a%20measuring%20cup%20to%20get%20the%20recipe%20just%20right.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20only%20part%20of%20Garten's%20recipe%20that%20actually%20requires%20a%20little%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hadn't%20bought%20pre-shredded%20fontina%20or%20pre-crumbled%20Gorgonzola%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20just%20grate%20them%20as%20well.%20And%20let%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20it%20was%20definitely%20an%20arm%20workout.%20Next%20time%2C%20I'll%20likely%20just%20finely%20chop%20the%20fontina%20instead%2C%20as%20its%20creamy%20texture%20made%20it%20a%20tad%20trickier%20to%20work%20with%20the%20grater.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20couldn't%20help%20admire%20all%20the%20beautiful%20cheeses%20in%20my%20mixing%20bowl.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f6509b057b7da001ee128b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221862%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20intrigued%20to%20see%20how%20all%20these%20cheeses%20would%20work%20together.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20creamy%20ricotta%20to%20the%20sharp%20Romano%2C%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20see%20how%20all%20these%20different%20flavors%20and%20textures%20would%20blend%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20I%20finally%20stopped%20staring%20at%20my%20cheese%2C%20I%20added%20the%20crushed%20tomatoes%20and%20heavy%20cream.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221507%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten's%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f63a30457b7da001ee1249a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221882%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20adding%20the%20cheeses%2C%20I%20threw%20in%20the%20additional%20ingredients.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20chopped%20up%20some%20basil%20to%20throw%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20just%20before%20I%20mixed%20everything%20together%2C%20I%20started%20cooking%20my%20pasta.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten's%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f63a30c323fc4001e0d6ec3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20parboiled%20my%20penne%20for%20four%20minutes.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20Garten's%20recipe%2C%20you're%20not%20actually%20supposed%20to%20fully%20cook%20the%20pasta.%20You%20just%20need%20to%20parboil%20the%20penne%20for%20four%20minutes%20in%20a%20pot%20of%20salted%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20dumped%20my%20pound%20of%20pasta%20into%20the%20pot%2C%20I%20set%20a%20timer%20and%20went%20back%20to%20my%20bowl%20of%20cheese.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20I%20mixed%20the%20cheesy%20sauce%2C%20I%20watched%20as%20it%20turned%20into%20a%20surprising%20shade%20of%20millennial%20pink.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten's%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f63a317323fc4001e0d6ec5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221435%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20loved%20the%20pale-pink%20color%20of%20the%20sauce%20mixture.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWho%20knew%20Garten's%20pasta%20would%20be%20so%20on-trend%3F%20The%20color%20was%20actually%20quite%20pretty%2C%20and%20not%20at%20all%20what%20I%20had%20expected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20draining%20my%20parboiled%20noodles%2C%20I%20put%20them%20back%20into%20the%20same%20pot%20and%20added%20my%20cheesy%20pink%20mixture.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten's%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f63a31b323fc4001e0d6ec9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20made%20sure%20all%20my%20penne%20noodles%20were%20submerged%20in%20the%20pink%20sauce.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarten%20recommends%20dividing%20your%20pasta%20into%20%26quot%3Bshallow%20ceramic%20gratin%20dishes.%26quot%3B%20I%20don't%20even%20own%20a%20proper%20stove%20pot%2C%20much%20less%20pretty%20cookware!%20But%20I%20realized%20that%20this%20dish%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-pot-meals-michelin-chefs-cook-at-home-2020-6%5C%22%3Eeasily%20turn%20into%20a%20one-pot%20recipe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20who%20doesn't%20love%20dealing%20with%20fewer%20dishes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20tossed%20the%20penne%20with%20the%20mixture%2C%20making%20sure%20all%20the%20noodles%20were%20submerged%20in%20the%20pretty%20pink%20pool%20of%20cheese.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20just%20before%20popping%20my%20pasta%20in%20the%20oven%2C%20I%20added%20some%20butter.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten's%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f63a31c323fc4001e0d6eca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20went%20against%20Garten's%20recipe%20and%20added%20far%20less%20butter.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20I%20love%20Garten%2C%20I%20have%20to%20admit%20that%20I%20went%20against%20her%20recipe%20on%20this%20last%20step.%20The%20%26quot%3BBarefoot%20Contessa%26quot%3B%20star%20recommends%20using%20half%20a%20stick%20(four%20tablespoons)%20of%20unsalted%20butter%20to%20dot%20your%20penne%20pasta%20with%2C%20which%20sounded%20very%20overwhelming%2C%20to%20be%20honest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20Molly%2C%20who%20is%20far%20more%20experienced%20in%20the%20kitchen%20than%20I%20am%2C%20confirmed%20that%20half%20a%20stick%20of%20butter%20would%20be%20too%20much%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20paired%20with%20all%20that%20cheese.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20recipe%20down%20to%20just%20one%20tablespoon%2C%20using%20a%20knife%20to%20shave%20off%20little%20knobs%20of%20butter%20that%20I%20sprinkled%20right%20on%20top%20of%20the%20pot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20took%20less%20than%2020%20minutes%20to%20bake%20the%20pasta.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten's%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f63a31b57b7da001ee124a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pasta%20has%20a%20gorgeous%20golden-brown%20color.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarten's%20recipe%20recommends%20cooking%20the%20pasta%20until%20it's%20%26quot%3Bbubbly%20and%20brown%26quot%3B%20on%20top%2C%20which%20she%20estimates%20will%20take%20around%20seven%20to%2010%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20waited%20for%20the%20pasta%20to%20cook%2C%20the%20delicious%20smell%20of%20cheese%20completely%20filled%20the%20kitchen.%20And%2C%20as%20the%20minutes%20ticked%20by%2C%20I%20could%20hear%20the%20penne%20start%20to%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20every%20oven%20is%20different.%20Overall%2C%20it%20took%20my%20pasta%20about%2017%20minutes%20total%20to%20bake.%20I%20waited%20until%20I%20could%20see%20that%20the%20penne%20in%20the%20center%20of%20my%20pan%20was%20turning%20brown%20before%20I%20took%20it%20out%2C%20ensuring%20it%20had%20cooked%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20pasta%20came%20out%20looking%20glorious.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten's%20penne%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f63a31957b7da001ee1249f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221629%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pasta%20was%20creamy%20and%20rich%20without%20being%20too%20heavy.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20millennial%20pink%20turned%20into%20a%20beautiful%20almost%20golden%20color%2C%20and%20there%20appeared%20to%20be%20an%20even%20crust%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20pasta.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chunks%20of%20mozzarella%20that%20had%20floated%20to%20the%20top%20made%20the%20dish%20look%20even%20more%20inviting.%20I%20already%20felt%20soothed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20it%20tasted%20so%20good%20we%20went%20back%20for%20seconds.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20penne%20dish%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f652d8d323fc4001e0d7437%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dish%20isn't%20meant%20to%20take%20too%20long%20in%20the%20oven.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3