%2Fwho-is-donald-trumps-ice-maiden-susie-mentioned-7-times-in-his-victory-speech%2Farticleshow%2F115027203.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115027203.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E66-year-old%20Susie%20Wiles%20was%20immersed%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%202024%20campaign.%20As%20Donald%20Trump%20described%20her%2C%20she%20is%20always%20in%20the%20background%20and%20likes%20to%20remain%20away%20from%20the%20limelight%20though%20she%20was%20with%20Trump%20at%20every%20crucial%20stop.%20Wiles%20traveled%20to%20Atlanta%20for%20the%20debate%2C%20flying%20to%20the%20event%20with%20Trump.%20She%20stayed%20with%20the%20former%20president%20as%20other%20campaign%20aides%2C%20and%20surrogates%20but%20she%20managed%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20limelight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-donald-trumps-ice-maiden-susie-mentioned-7-times-in-his-victory-speech%2Farticleshow%2F115027203.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-donald-trumps-ice-maiden-susie-mentioned-7-times-in-his-victory-speech%2Famp_articleshow%2F115027203.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-donald-trumps-ice-maiden-susie-mentioned-7-times-in-his-victory-speech%2Famp_articleshow%2F115027203.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harris%20To%20Concede%20Defeat%20To%20Trump%20Early%20Tomorrow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20and%20Democratic%20nominee%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20deliver%20a%20speech%20conceding%20defeat%20in%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20to%20Republican%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20will%20deliver%20the%20speech%20at%204%20pm%20local%20time%20(2.30%20am%20IST%20on%20Thursday)%20at%20Howard%20University%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20had%20cancelled%20her%20election%20night%20speech%20after%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20former%20president%20Trump%20would%20cross%20the%20magic%20mark%20of%20270%20electoral%20college%20votes%20and%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%20as%20the%2047th%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20polls%20predicting%20that%20the%20election%20was%20too%20close%20to%20call%2C%20Trump%20steamrolled%20Harris%20and%20went%20on%20to%20pick%20up%20key%20swing%20states%2C%20including%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Georgia%20and%20Wisconsin%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20his%20return%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20won%20the%20popular%20vote%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Republican%20to%20do%20so%20in%2020%20years%2C%20after%20George%20W%20Bush%20in%202004.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20a%20victory%20speech%20to%20a%20room%20full%20of%20roaring%20supporters%20in%20Florida%2C%20Trump%20said%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20has%20given%20us%20an%20unprecedented%20and%20powerful%20mandate%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPowerful%2C%20Unsuccessful%20Campaign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%2C%20who%20had%20224%20electoral%20college%20votes%20as%20of%20Wednesday%20night%20against%20Trump's%20280%2C%20ran%20a%20powerful%20campaign%20in%20her%20bid%20to%20become%20the%20first%20woman%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20The%2060-year-old%20former%20prosecutor%20also%20made%20history%20as%20the%20first%20black%20woman%20and%20the%20first%20South%20Asian%20woman%20to%20get%20the%20presidential%20nomination%20from%20a%20major%20party.%20She%20raised%20%241%20billion%20in%20less%20than%20three%20months%20and%20was%20endorsed%20by%20celebrities%20like%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%20Beyonce%20and%20Oprah%20as