minal-charges-what-happens-now-he-has-won-us-election-13249511%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Maharashtra%2C%20Ruling%20Alliance's%2010%20Guarantees%20Vs%20Opposition's%20%26quot%3BPanch%20Sutra%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20raining%20poll%20promises%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20with%20around%20two%20weeks%20to%20go%20before%20the%20assembly%20election.%20The%20ruling%20alliance%20Mahayuti%20and%20the%20Opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20have%20both%20released%20their%20manifestos%20which%20make%20tall%20promises%2C%20especially%20to%20the%20women%2C%20farmers%20and%20the%20young%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20do-or-die%20nature%20of%20the%20coming%20battle%2C%20parties%20like%20Shiv%20Sena%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20or%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20released%20individual%20manifestos%20and%20made%20election%20announcements%20for%20every%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20is%20wooing%20voters%20with%20its%2010%20guarantees%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20people%20with%20a%20%26quot%3BPanchsutra%26quot%3B%20(Letter%20of%20five%20promises)%20in%20its%20joint%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahayuti's%2010%20guarantees%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20Increasing%20the%20amount%20of%20Ladli%20Behan%20Yojana%20from%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%202%2C100%20and%20a%20promise%20to%20deploy%2025%2C000%20women%20in%20the%20police%20force.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20Farmers%20guaranteed%20loan%20waiver%20and%20under%20the%20Kisan%20Samman%20Yojana%2C%20the%20amount%20to%20increase%20from%20Rs%2012%2C000%20to%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20A%2020%25%20subsidy%20on%20MSP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20Old-age%20pension%20increase%20from%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20Rs%202%2C100%20per%20month%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fl