will%20be%20conducted%2C%20in%20which%20an%20attempt%20will%20be%20made%20to%20remove%20the%2050%25%20reservation%20limit.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Health%20insurance%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20and%20free%20medicines%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Financial%20assistance%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%204%2C000%20per%20month%20for%20unemployed%20young%20people.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BConstitution%20in%20danger%26quot%3B%20narrative%20had%20given%20a%20big%20advantage%20to%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi.%20This%20time%20too%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20seen%20waving%20the%20Red%20Book%20of%20the%20Constitution%20in%20Nagpur%20and%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20joined%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20the%20Red%20Book%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20brought%20was%20completely%20blank%2C%20and%20called%20it%20an%20insult%20to%20Baba%20Saheb%20Ambedkar's%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730911380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F4h75fsog_mva-manifesto_625x300_06_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-maharashtra-ruling-alliances-10-guarantees-vs-oppositions-panch-sutra-6959562%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20raining%20poll%20promises%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20with%20around%20two%20weeks%20to%20go%20before%20the%20assembly%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20Kamala%20Harris's%20Historic%20White%20House%20Bid%20Fell%20Short%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20meeting%20with%20one%20of%20America's%20most%20powerful%20unions%20in%20September%20at%20its%20Washington%20headquarters%2C%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris