Cn%3Cp%3ERajwinder%20has%20been%20teaching%20at%20the%20school%20for%20six%20months%2C%20embracing%20her%20role%20with%20enthusiasm%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose.%20Each%20day%2C%20she%20walks%20into%20the%20classroom%2C%20ready%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20her%20students%2C%20who%20comprise%20people%20aged%20between%2050%20and%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Rajwinder%20shares%20insights%20into%20why%20many%20elderly%20residents%20missed%20out%20on%20education%20earlier%20in%20life.%20She%20emphasised%20how%20the%20Bebe%20Bapu%20School%20has%20been%20a%20catalyst%20for%20transformation%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360205%2Fold-age-home-in-gujarat-laljibhai-prajapati-shri-navchetan-andhjan-mandal-disabled-people-senior-citizens-kachchh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eempowering%20the%20eld%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360205%2Fold-age-home-in-gujarat-laljibhai-prajapati-shri-navchetan-andhjan-mandal-disabled-people-senior-citizens-kachchh%2F%5C%22%3Eerly%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20skills%20they%20need%20to%20survive.%20Additionally%2C%20she%20focuses%20on%20her%20future%20goals%2C%20emphasising%20her%20vision%20for%20continuing%20to%20uplift%20her%20community%20through%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDevelopment%20of%20a%20diverse%20learning%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajwinder%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20factors%20contributing%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20education%20among%20the%20elders.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20primary%20reason%20many%20elders%20missed%20out%20on%20education%20in%20their%20early%20years%20is%20that%20educational%20opportunities%20were%20scarce%2C%20and%20there%20was%20little%20societal%20emphasis%20on%20learning.%20People%20were%20often%20preoccupied%20with%20household%20responsibilities%2C