0was%20providing%20quality%20care%20in%20the%20hinterlands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%2C%20and%20along%20with%20the%20other%20two%20co-founders%2C%20set%20up%20the%20first%20VitusCare%20dialysis%20centre%20in%20Aligarh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20was%20very%20clear%3A%20we%20wanted%20quality%20dialysis%20therapy%20centres%20in%20cities%20which%20lack%20accessibility.%20Due%20to%20the%20distance%2C%20people%20often%20miss%20their%20dialysis%20sessions%2C%20leading%20to%20poor%20outcomes.%20In%20India%2C%20a%20CKD%20patient%20on%20dialysis%20lives%2C%20on%20average%2C%20for%20four%20years%2C%20while%20in%20the%20West%2C%20patients%20live%20for%20over%2015%20years.%20We%20need%20to%20improve%20outcomes%20for%20our%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Prabhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChronic%20kidney%20disease%20(CKD)%20affects%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20although%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20patients%20remains%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Founders%20Prabhat%20Shrivastava%2C%20Pankaj%20Tandon%20and%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal%20(L-R)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20h