dent%20that%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20practices%20and%20business%20models%20would%20also%20ensure%20economic%20growth%20for%20the%20farmers%20as%20well%20as%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%20This%20soil%20incorporation%20will%20have%20long-term%20benefits%20for%20improving%20the%20quality%20of%20soil%2C%20increasing%20water-use%20efficiency%2C%20and%20reducing%20the%20intensity%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%20being%20used.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20doubt%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20innovative%2C%20boasting%20a%20quick%20and%20radical%20alternative%20to%20burning%20the%20stubble.%20While%20being%20in%20synergy%20with%20Merino%20Industries%E2%80%99%20commitment%20to%20the%20environment%2C%20the%20process%20utilises%20electricity%20only%20during%20the%20size%20reduction%20of%20paddy%20straw%20and%20the%20rendered%20compost%20also%20improves%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20soil%20it%20is%20added%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20proud%20to%20create%20%26amp%3B%20collaborate%20with%20VNIT%20at%20the%20Merino%20Innovation%20Center%20within%20the%20campus%2C%20which%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20how%20academia%20and%20industry%20can%20unite%20to%20create%20meaningful%2C%20problem-solving%20solutions.%20The%20encouraging%20results%20from%20our%20test%20beds%20give%20us%20confidence%20in%20expanding%20these%20practices%20across%20the%20farmlands%20in%20order%20to%20address%20critical%20air%20quality%20issues%20from%20stubble%20burning.%20This%20initiative%20aligns%20with%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20mission%20of%20promoting%20Universal%20Weal%20through%20trade%20and%20industry%2C%20contributing%20to%20both%20environmental%20and%20societal%20well-being%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mr%20Lohia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20hre