jects%20with%20directors%20like%20Anurag%20Kashyap.%20I%20learnt%20the%20basics%20of%20writing%2C%20editing%20and%20producing%20shows%20during%20my%20stint%20at%20MTV%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20was%20just%20before%20the%20digital%20medium%20took%20off.%20His%20series%20for%20MTV%20%E2%80%93%20Reality%20Stars%2C%20although%20well-received%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%20commercially.%20Just%2025%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20cope%20with%20this%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20toast%20of%20MTV.%20Everyone%20hyped%20me%20up%20and%20pushed%20me.%20When%20the%20series%20was%20launched%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20there%20was%20complete%20silence.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20tools%20or%20resources%20to%20handle%20the%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20retrospect%2C%20he%20acknowledges%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20handle%20it%20well.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20anxious%20for%20almost%20three%20to%20four%20months.%20To%20cope%2C%20I%20buried%20myself%20in%20work%20and%20started%20using%20my%20subsequent%20wins%20as%20a%20distraction.%20I%20kept%20telling%20myself%20that%20I%20was%20fine%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits%20candidly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESociety%20often%20fails%20to%20teach%20us%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20handle%20failure%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Nikhil%20continued%20to%20work%2C%20soon%20landing%20his%20dream%20job%20at%20Yash%20Raj%20Films