0Salaam%20Baalak%20Trust%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20providing%20support%20for%20street%20children%20%E2%80%94%20lauds%20the%20ones%20conducted%20for%20children.%20These%2C%20he%20says%2C%20tackle%20malnourishment%2C%20a%20prevalent%20concern%20seen%20in%20children%20whose%20parents%20are%20daily%20wage%20workers%20or%20live%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20and%20do%20not%20have%20the%20time%20or%20knowledge%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20diets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20health%20camps%20focus%20on%20encouraging%20parents%20to%20recalibrate%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20dietary%20needs%20while%20not%20exceeding%20their%20budget%20constraints.%20In%20the%20past%20year%20alone%2C%20the%20mobile%20health%20vans%20have%20reached%20out%20to%2035%2C224%20people%20from%20across%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20unabridged%20access%20to%20healthcare%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20patients%20filter%20into%20the%20different%20speciality%20rooms%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20it%20is%20fascinating%20to%20watch%20their%20worry%20morph%20into%20relief%20after%20their%20consultation.%20They%20know%20they%20are%20in%20safe%20hands.%20Dr%20Rahul%20Joshi%2C%20consulting%20homoeopathic%2C%20credits%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20investigative%20procedures%20backed%20by%20credible%20diagnostics%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20setup%20welcomes%20everyone%20in%20tune%20with%20our%20Indian%20ideology%20of%20secularism.%20There%20is%20no%20bias%20anywhere%2C%20we%20have%20patients%20from%20all%20communities%20coming%20here.%20The%20ethos%20is%20of%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underscores%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20must%20agree%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThe%20overall%20setup%20looks%20very%20corporate.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20rundown%20one%2C%20which%20we%20observe%20in%20most%20of%20the%20places%20offering%20free%20treatment.%20Top%20doctors%20consult%20here.%20The%20primary%20aim%20is%20accessibility%20to%20the%20best%20doctors%20with%20regular%20follow-ups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-3-1730122083.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homoeopathic%20team%20led%20by%20Dr%20Rahul%20Joshi%20provides%20alternative%20medicine%20counselling%20to%20patients%20for%20several%20conditions.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-3-1730122083.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-3-1730122083-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-3-1730122083-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-3-1730122083-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-3-1730122083-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-372669%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homoeopathic%20team%20led%20by%20Dr%20Rahul%20Joshi%20provides%20alternative%20medicine%20counselling%20to%20patients%20for%20several%20conditions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20physical%20health%20concerns%20deserve%20attention%2C%20mental%20health%20too%20demands%20a%20listening%20ear.%20And%20the%20counselling%20unit%20is%20a%20vibrant%20space%20where%20every%20child%20is%20treated%20with%20care%20and%20compassion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20enter%2C%20we%20are%20met%20with%20a%20visual%20of%20Ira%20(4)%20attempting%20to%20string%20thread%20into%20a%20cardboard%20cutout%20while%20her%20counsellor%20looks%20on%2C%20pitching%20in%20when%20needed.%20Ira%E2%80%99s%20mother%20is%20amused%20by%20how%20her%20little%20girl%20has%20tak